commit.message: Let's move to a more readable format
Handle unintelligible expectation files somewhat better.
Don't die horribly if the expectation file doesn't exist.
The big 1.0 rewrite and drop of the 0.x formats.
Cheat and use msgpack to avoid pickle bugs.
Move the default expectation file location to the test root.
Rewrite all the unicode/bytes mungling; 0.10 (still beta)
This should be commited so we're actually a package.
Fix to only include *failed* collections as failures.
Fix so expectations actually get written.
Ignore sessionfinish if it happens to be called on slave threads.
